Class GetMyeBayBuyingRequestType

java.lang.Object
  com.ebay.soap.eBLBaseComponents.AbstractRequestType
      com.ebay.soap.eBLBaseComponents.GetMyeBayBuyingRequestType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class GetMyeBayBuyingRequestType
extends AbstractRequestType
implements Serializable

Returns items from the Buying section of the user's My eBay account, including items that the user is watching, bidding on, has won, has not won, and has made best offers on.
